fields.title: Answer
fields.value: QueenA is the original prophet who was the sent from the future by accident into 2018 and in order to figure out when she will return back to her original timeline, she kept asking wen 6 dolla to check if she is back to her original timeline. The $6 prophecy was eventually fulfilled on 15.08.2020. and we now celebrate that day every year as QueenA $6 day.
